# real deployment procedure
1. Copy `secrets/secrets.env.example` into the decrypted contents of `secrets/secrets.age`.
2. Set real values for `APP_KEY` and `TF_VAR_hcloud_token`.
3. If needed, adjust `TF_VAR_nixos_config_name` and `TF_VAR_hcloud_ssh_key_name`.
4. Ensure the Hetzner SSH key named by `TF_VAR_hcloud_ssh_key_name` already exists in your Hetzner account.
5. Rekey or re-encrypt `secrets/secrets.age` so your local user key can decrypt it.
6. Run `nix run .#deploy_adonisjs_host_template` for the first remote deployment.
7. Run `bash prm/post-deploy.sh` to fetch the new host SSH public key into `prm/<host>.pub` and rekey `secrets.age`.
8. Run `nix run .#deploy_adonisjs_host_template` again so the deployed host can decrypt the rekeyed secret.
